{{Han compound|金|𢧤|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=metal}}. The original version, according to the Shuowen Jiezi, is [[𨮯]], with 大 on top, hence the original phonetic component should be not [[𢧜]].

===Etymology===
{{etymon|zh|id=iron|:inh|sit-pro:*hljak<id:iron>}}
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*hljak||iron}}. Cognate with {{cog|bo|ལྕགས}}. According to the ''{{w|Shuowen}}'', alternative forms included {{och-l|銕}}. Compare {{och-l|驖|black horse}}.

